snippet.title: BIG Summer Book Haul (20+ Books!)│by Amber Burns
snippet.description:
Will I ever get caught up on my TBR? No! But will I enjoy the process? ABSOLUTELY!! Let me know your thoughts on organizing larger hauls this way.

0:00 Intro
0:15 New Approach to Haul Videos
1:42 Short Stories & Graphic Novels
5:15 Nonfiction
6:07 Romance
9:30 Literary Fiction
16:55 Fantasy/Sci-Fi (YA)
24:47 Wrap up
